values:
HAPPY BIRTHDAY to me!

it's officially monday and it's my birthday. 
i need to go to sleep though b.c. i have to work early, which will result in me being able to leave early. oh yay!

okie..off to bed i go.
happy birthday to me.

la la la making burritos
la la la eating my burritos
la la la running around my house straightening up
la la la checking email
la la la let's watch a movie!
la la la let's have some coffee!
la la la...oh.. kitchen is kind of hot, why's that?
la la la.....holy shit i left the burner on. browning pan still on the fire.....

this would be an hour after i was making my burritos....
so caught up in the wonderful yumminess of burritos that i forgot to turn off the stove. 
my gas stove.

slinks away in shame
